    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款支持多人<strong>联机跑团</strong>游戏的<strong>免费</strong>工具。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个Demo中，你可以用它来制作自己的模组冒险、与朋友联机游玩，亦或是当成一个车卡工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Demo版本已支持P2p联机</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demo中还能体验到一下特点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绘制地图</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭建故事发生的场景，内置多种风格的地图部件，也支持自己导入图片材质和模型（Demo已可以体验到此功能）。支持格子地图，并且可以自定义格子大小。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras/5f339c1d73a9111842a65017cc8fec29.avif?t=1736851686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras_big/5f339c1d73a9111842a65017cc8fec29.avif?t=1736851686 width=800 height=454 /></span> </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绘制户外地形，改变场景内的日照时间和天气，支持多种天气，包括晴天、多云、雨雪等。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras/ae17ad238a062f01222a0d41422d2878.avif?t=1736851686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras_big/ae17ad238a062f01222a0d41422d2878.avif?t=1736851686 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可提前设置玩家调查物体会发生的事件，减少主持人复制成功失败文本的时间。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras/63d7c79b859a8a8c580f66cbffbd75c4.avif?t=1736851686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras_big/63d7c79b859a8a8c580f66cbffbd75c4.avif?t=1736851686 width=800 height=454 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聊天窗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有内置聊天框，可进行骰点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras/bda291a9e4df11c400d560169339edfb.avif?t=1736851686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras_big/bda291a9e4df11c400d560169339edfb.avif?t=1736851686 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创建角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高自由度的捏人，可调节身高、胖瘦、脸型以及颜色，让你轻松捏出app15的食尸鬼外貌。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结团后可收藏自己的角色卡，GM允许的情况下可在新团复用老卡，养成经历丰富多彩的PC。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras/f8467e355459662483053b88ead1dce4.avif?t=1736851686\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231730/extras_big/f8467e355459662483053b88ead1dce4.avif?t=1736851686 width=800 height=452 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
